      <title outputclass="H4ForH3_10" class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.223-9</ph> Estimate of Percentage of Recovered Material Content for EPA-Designated Items.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p otherprops="Body"
            outputclass="Body"
            class="- topic/p "
            id="d3359e13">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1094741.dita#i1094741"
                     base="i1094741"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">23.406</xref>(d)</ph>, insert the following clause:</p>
         <p otherprops="Ctr_SmCaps" outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p ">Estimate of Percentage of Recovered Material Content for EPA-Designated Items (May 2008)</p>
         <ol id="d3341e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3359e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definitions</i>. As used in this clause-</p>
               <p id="d3359e38" class="- topic/p ">“Postconsumer material” means a material or finished product that has served its intended use and has been discarded for disposal or recovery, having completed its life as a consumer item. Postconsumer material is a part of the broader category of “recovered material.”</p>
               <p id="d3359e41" class="- topic/p ">“Recovered material” means waste materials and by-products recovered or diverted from solid waste, but the term does not include those materials and by-products generated from, and commonly reused within, an original manufacturing process.</p>
            </li>
            <li otherprops="abc" outputclass="H5_abc" class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3359e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  The Contractor, on completion of this contract, shall-</p>
               <ol id="d3341e56" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3359e57" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        Estimate the percentage of the total recovered material content for EPA-designated item(s) delivered and/or used in contract performance, including, if applicable, the percentage of post-consumer material content; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li otherprops="123" outputclass="H6_123" class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3359e66" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        Submit this estimate to _____________________ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Contracting Officer complete in accordance with agency procedures</i>].</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p otherprops="Body_Endofclause" class="- topic/p ">(End of clause)</p>
         <section outputclass="Alternate" class="- topic/section "><?FM MARKER [Alt] Start?>
            <p otherprops="Body"
               outputclass="H_Body"
               class="- topic/p "
               id="d3359e85">
               <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Alternate I (<i otherprops="SmallCaps" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">May</i>2008)</i>. As prescribed in <ph outputclass="AlternateXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
                  <xref href="FAR-i1094741.dita#i1094741"
                        base="i1094741"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">23.406</xref>
               </ph>(d), redesignate paragraph (b) of the basic clause as paragraph (c) and add the following paragraph (b) to the basic clause:</p>
            <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_List1"
               outputclass="H_Body"
               class="- topic/p ">(b) The Contractor shall execute the following certification required by the Resource Conservation and Recovery Act of1976 (<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                     format="html"
                     scope="external"
                     class="- topic/xref ">42 U.S.C.6962(i)(2)(C)</xref>):</p>
            <p otherprops="Ctr_SmCaps" outputclass="H_Body" class="- topic/p ">Certification</p>
            <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
               outputclass="H_Body"
               class="- topic/p ">I, _______________ (name of certifier), am an officer or employee responsible for the performance of this contract and hereby certify that the percentage of recovered material content for EPA-designated items met the applicable contract specifications or other contractual requirements.</p>
            <p otherprops="Body_Alternate_NoIndent"
               outputclass="H_Body"
               class="- topic/p ">__________________________________________________ [<i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Signature of the Officer or Employee</i>]</p>
